name: Lost Frequencies
description: '''Felix De Laet''' (born 30 November 1993), known by his [[stage name]] '''Lost Frequencies''', is a Belgian [[Disc jockey|DJ]] and [[record producer]]. He is best known for his [[Single (music)|singles]] "[[Are You with Me#Lost Frequencies version|Are You with Me]]" in 2014, "[[Reality (Lost Frequencies song)|Reality]]" featuring [[Janieck Devy]] in 2015, and "[[Where Are You Now (Lost Frequencies song)|Where Are You Now]]" with [[Calum Scott]] in 2021.
